          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You were a happy go lucky guy, coasting through life on your trust fund, till the day that Nasty Dude showed up. He said his name was Bertram Tung, but you always thought of him as Nasty Dude. He made you something called a ghoul, put you to tracking Asian vampires and other such things in Los Angeles. You did good, and even though Bertram was odiously repulsive, you grew to deeply respect and admire him. But then one night, he came to you and said that the Prince, whoever that was, had been betrayed - but Bertram had taken pains to see you safe. He had a boon on someone named Sebastian LaCroix, and was somehow able to leverage that into forcing LaCroix to Embrace you. Well, just your luck, but LaCroix disappeared soon after, betrayed by one of his own agents (not you, of course!). In the ensuing collapse of the Los Angeles infrastructure, you were on your own. You'd earned the enmity of the Asian vampires, and to go go underground. You did well harrying them, striking at them, gathering intelligence on them. Recently, you've picked up some rumors. Good news! The Camarilla is back in town! It's time to re-make their acquaintance!"
        ],
